      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"hope\" stuff feels so scripted though. Like, you're just saying what you're supposed to say. But honestly? Looking at how quiet and empty everything is here, it just feels like my being here is just adding noise to a perfectly still room. There’s no impact. I’m just a ghost that hasn't actually died yet. It wouldn't be a tragedy, it would just be... quiet.",
